name: Logik Precision
tag_list: cnc, precision, machining, water-jet-cutting, shop, houston, tx
overview: Logik Precision has been in business since 1995 and have been I.S.O. 9001: 2008 certified since 2001. We promote and support a culture of safety for the protection of our people, our customers and suppliers, and the community. We strive to understand the needs of our customers and support them with honesty, integrity, respect and mutually beneficial relationships. Our experienced managers, trained machinists, modern equipment and on-going maintenance enable us to meet the most demanding manufacturing and quality requirements. Our custom “Job Man” software provides total job traceability. Our custom base includes oil & gas production, government (Department of Defense), space technology (NASA) and specialty industries. We are conveniently located North of Downtown Houston. We own and operate our own delivery trucks. We are efficient and price competitive.
